<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Image icons (webp, png, svg) render as actual images across note sheets, BigCal, week blocks, chronicle, HUD, and tooltips</li>
      <li>Schedule tab has an explicit One-time / Recurring mode toggle with per-mode controls</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Cardinal Weights grid in the climate zone editor now localizes direction initials</li>
      <li>Festival duration blowout from yearZero offset mismatch</li>
      <li>Festival definitions wiped when the note cleanup pass pruned duplicates</li>
      <li>Recurring notes inheriting an inflated span from endDate</li>
      <li>Single-day note moves not syncing endDate with startDate, inflating duration</li>
      <li>Removed-calendar renames now migrate stored overrides and note/folder flags</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Changes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Festival editing moved to the note sheet; Calendar editor Festival tab is read-only</li>
      <li>Festival metadata stored on <code>linkedFestival</code> notes; <code>calendar.festivals</code> is seed-only</li>
      <li>Simple Calendar and Mini Calendar importers create festival notes directly</li>
      <li>Show Bookends moved to Settings tab; Duration moved to Schedule tab</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
